---
# SumelaOS per-developer overrides (PERSONAL — never committed).
#
# Copy this file to `.sumela/local.md` (gitignored) to set YOUR own preferences
# without changing the team-wide project config in AGENTS.md:
#
#   cp .sumela/local.md.example .sumela/local.md
#
# Only the keys listed below are honored. Anything else is ignored.

# Interaction language — the language the agent talks to YOU in (explanations,
# questions, status, the Context Manifest header). Overrides AGENTS.md Section 2's
# project default for your clone only.
interaction_language: English
---

<!--
  Why only interaction_language?

  Code NAMING and code DOCUMENTATION languages are deliberately NOT overridable
  here — they must stay consistent across the whole team, so they live only in
  AGENTS.md Section 2 (committed, team-wide). This file changes how the agent
  speaks to you, never what lands in the shared codebase.
-->
